### Prefixed values
Use the `prefix` parameter to specify the abbreviated prefix unit e.g. '£', and the `title` parameter to specify the full name of the prefix unit e.g. 'Pounds (GBP)'.
{{
    patternlibExample({"path": "components/input/examples/prefixed/index.njk"})
}}

### Suffixed values 
Use the `suffix` parameter to specify the abbreviated suffix unit e.g. '%', and the `title` parameter to specify the full name of the suffix unit e.g. 'Percent'.
